library(exscidata)
library(ggplot2)
library(broom)
library(knitr)
data("hypertrophy")

dat <- hypertrophy %>%
  select(PARTICIPANT, SQUAT_3RM, PERCENT_TYPE_II_T1) %>%
  print()

ggplot(dat, aes(SQUAT_3RM, PERCENT_TYPE_II_T1)) + 
  geom_point(size = 3, fill = "lightblue", shape = 21) +
  labs(x = "Squat 3RM (kg)", 
       y = "Type II fibres (%)") +
  theme_minimal() 

m1 <- lm(SQUAT_3RM ~ PERCENT_TYPE_II_T1, data = dat)

summary(m1)
